data.description: Newly renovated 2 unit property located in BERWYN! New electrical, plumbing, windows, doors, kitchens and baths! New boiler and high efficiency water heaters. Granite countertops & stainless steel appliances. Hardwood floors, separate utilities and laundry area. Newly painted 2 car garage and large backyard. Unit 1 consists of 2 nice sized bedrooms, 1 bathroom, living and dining area with a tastefully renovated kitchen. Unit 2 is offering 3 large bedrooms, 1 bathroom, living and dining area with beautiful hardwood floors throughout. Easy to rent or live in one unit while the other pays the mortgage! There is room to increase rents.
